Feature: Delete comment from moodle forum

    Scenario: Student views a comment on the forum
    Given Student is loggged in 
    And a forum with at least one comment
    When the student navigates to the forum thread
    Then the student should see the comment


   Scenario: Teacher deletes a comment from the forum
    Given Teacher logged in as an admin
    And a forum with at least one thread
    When the teacher selects the comment for deletion
    And confirms the deletion action
    Then the comment should no longer appear in the forum thread